This project uses Next.js App Router.

Global rules:
- Always prefer SSG or SSR. Never use SPA-only rendering unless explicitly requested.
- Use Server Components by default. Add "use client" only when strictly necessary.
- Always implement proper SEO:
  - Use Next.js Metadata API for title, description, OpenGraph, and Twitter tags.
- Prioritize performance and Core Web Vitals:
  - Minimize JavaScript sent to the client.
  - Avoid unnecessary hydration.
- Use shadcn/ui components only from /components/ui.
- Do not reimplement UI components manually.
- Assume the site must be fast, Google-indexable, and production-ready.
- Use font 'Unbounded',Arial,sans-serif
- Use shadcn MCP